OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781806274
OL,3,CStrep B campaigner hopeful of
OL,4,Cbreakthrough in national testing
OL,6,F"I will probably sleep better that
OL,7,Fnight than ever... knowing that babies
OL,8,Fare going to be safe," says Jane Plumb.
OL,10,F"With all screening programmes it's
OL,11,Fabout a choice and that should be
OL,12,Fexactly the same for Group B Strep."
OL,14,FJane lost her baby, Theo, not even 24
OL,15,Fhours after giving birth. He had been
OL,16,Finfected with Group B Strep, a type of
OL,17,Fbacteria which lives in between two to
OL,18,Ffour out of every 10 women in the UK.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
