FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781806274
OL,3,CStrep B campaigner hopeful of
OL,4,Cbreakthrough in national testing
OL,6,FIn the more than three decades since
OL,7,FTheo's death, Jane has campaigned for
OL,8,Fgreater awareness and prevention of
OL,9,Ffurther deaths linked to the bacteria.
OL,11,FSpeaking to ITV Meridian from the
OL,12,Foffices of Group B Strep Support - a
OL,13,Fcharity which she founded - in
OL,14,FHaywards Heath, East Sussex, Jane said
OL,15,Fshe's more hopeful of a breakthrough
OL,16,Fin nationwide testing than ever before.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
