OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781806274
OL,3,CStrep B campaigner hopeful of
OL,4,Cbreakthrough in national testing
OL,6,FInfection from the bacteria kills
OL,7,Faround one baby every week in the UK,
OL,8,Fwhile another will be left with a
OL,9,Flifelong disability.
OL,11,FBut the NHS says the risk is extremely
OL,12,Fsmall and, currently, it doesn't
OL,13,Frecommend routine testing because it
OL,14,Fsays that, even if a mother tests
OL,15,Fpositive for Group B Strep, it's not
OL,16,Fguaranteed whether her baby will
OL,17,Fbecome infected.
OL,19,FJane, however, says change is needed
OL,20,Fto help prevent further tragedy.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781806274
OL,3,CStrep B campaigner hopeful of
OL,4,Cbreakthrough in national testing
OL,6,F"The UK is a high income country...
OL,7,Fand our rate is double the rate in the
OL,8,FUnited States," she said.
OL,10,F"We know what we could be doing to
OL,11,Fstop most of these infections
OL,12,Fhappening and we're still not doing
OL,13,Fit."
OL,15,FIt's a view shared by her eldest son,
OL,16,FOliver Plumb, who helps support the
OL,17,Fwork of Group B Strep Support.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1781806274
OL,3,CStrep B campaigner hopeful of
OL,4,Cbreakthrough in national testing
OL,6,FHe told ITV Meridian that the current
OL,7,Fapproach is "quite weighted towards
OL,8,Ftreating a baby once they get sick",
OL,9,Fadding: "While most babies will make a
OL,10,Ffull recovery, even if they develop a
OL,11,FGroup B Strep infection, sometimes,
OL,12,Fsadly it's too late.
OL,14,F"You look at the UK's rates of
OL,15,Finfection, we're not doing well. Our
OL,16,Frate has continued to rise over about
OL,17,Fthe last 25, 30 years."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
